    • copy

      public InsnNode copy()
      Make copy of InsnNode object.
      NOTE: can't copy instruction with result argument (SSA variable can't be used in two different assigns).
      Prefer use next methods:
      • copyWithoutResult() to explicitly state that result not needed
      • copy(RegisterArg) to provide new result arg
      • copyWithNewSsaVar(MethodNode) to make new SSA variable for result arg
